OL,3,CPeston: Unnerving questions about the
OL,4,CAfghan data breach debacle
OL,6,FAs I said on News at Ten last night,
OL,7,Famong the disturbing issues and
OL,8,Fquestions raised by the life-
OL,9,Fendangering data leak are:
OL,11,FFirst, how a special forces reservist
OL,12,Fwould have had access to such a huge
OL,13,Ffile of sensitive data and the ability
OL,14,Fto email it - albeit unintentionally
OL,15,Fand by accident - without anyone in
OL,16,Fauthority knowing of the security
OL,17,Fbreach for a staggering 18 months?
