OL,3,CPeston: Unnerving questions about the
OL,4,CAfghan data breach debacle
OL,6,FSecond, why Ben Wallace as Defence
OL,7,FSecretary thought an injunction
OL,8,Fpreventing publication of the detail
OL,9,Fof the debacle would be adequate to
OL,10,Fprotect the safety of the Afghans
OL,11,Fnamed in the file? But then his
OL,12,Fsuccessor Grant Shapps asked the court
OL,13,Ffor a super injunction, preventing any
OL,14,Fmention even of the existence of the
OL,15,Finjunction.
