OL,3,CPeston: Unnerving questions about the
OL,4,CAfghan data breach debacle
OL,6,FAnd third, why it took the current
OL,7,FLabour government more than a year to
OL,8,Fcomplete a review allowing the super
OL,9,Finjunction to be lifted? Which is
OL,10,Flonger than the super injunction was
OL,11,Fin existence under the Tories.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FThe most upsetting question relates
OL,19,Fboth to the panicked decision to
OL,20,Fimpose the secrecy order in August
OL,21,F2023 and yesterday's lifting of it.
