OL,3,CPeston: Unnerving questions about the
OL,4,CAfghan data breach debacle
OL,6,FIf ministers and officials were so
OL,7,Fconfident then that lives would be
OL,8,Fendangered, how - with all the
OL,9,Fpublicity of the past 24 hours - can
OL,10,Fthey really be confident that the
OL,11,FTaliban won't exact revenge and
OL,12,Fretribution today, since by no means
OL,13,Fall those at risk have been
OL,14,Fclandestinely relocated to the UK?
OL,16,FIn the history of failure by the
OL,17,Fmachinery of the British state, this
OL,18,Fenters the hall of shame as a prime
OL,19,Fexhibit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
